<div><div><h2>Piramal Enterprises plans to raise up to Rs 1,000 cr via NCDs</h2></div><div>"piramal enterprises wednesday said it plans to raise up to rs 1000 crore through issue of secured non-convertible debentures (ncds) on private placement basis.the administrative committee of the board approved issue of secured ncds on private placement basis up to rs 500 crore with an option to retain over-subscription of up to rs 500 crore aggregating the total issue size to rs 1000 crores in two series the company said in a filing to the bse.the issue size of series 1 is rs 100 crore it added.the size of series 2 is rs 400 crore with green shoe option of rs 500 crore so that the total value shall not exceed rs 900 crore piramal enterprises said.the company however did not specify what it wants to do with the funds to be raised."</div></div>